{"tid":46471,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[錯台重開]新手投資求生指南 (一)","createTime":"2016-12-19T16:31:45.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-24T14:48:11.000Z","uid":30791,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3ab1da9f9b835624e884591f55ba0d43ac0eeb41","tid":46471,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:31:45.000Z","msg":"呢度講既投資係價值投資法(value investing)。<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Value investing is buying securities at a significant discount to their underlying value and holding them unitl their value is realized.&quot; - Seth Klarman<br />\n<br />\n對於投資新手，我會介紹佢地首先睇以下呢本書：<br />\nThe Element of Investing, by Burton G. Malkiel and Charles D. Ellis<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Elements-Investing-Lessons-Every-Investor/dp/1118484878\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FElements-Investing-Lessons-Every-Investor%2Fdp%2F1118484878&d=4y26Nzl7bms%2FR0TUX1plypkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=f54498a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.com/Elements-Investing-Lessons-Every-Investor/dp/1118484878</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://books.google.com.hk/books/about/The_Elements_of_Investing.html?id=oYtgNmQOQggC&amp;redir_esc=y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com.hk%2Fbooks%2Fabout%2FThe_Elements_of_Investing.html%3Fid%3DoYtgNmQOQggC%26redir_esc%3Dy&d=4y26Nzl7bms%2FR0TUX1plypkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=555cf9e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://books.google.com.hk/books/about/The_Elements_of_Investing.html?id=oYtgNmQOQggC&amp;redir_esc=y</a><br />\n<br />\n我唔太清楚 Ellis 係邊個。至於 Malkiel 比較為人熟悉既作品係 A random walk down wall street. 我是不同意 Malkiel 的觀點的，之後有機會再講到。<br />\n<br />\n講番 The Element of Investing (EOI) 呢本書。EOI 講既係點樣穩妥地投資。簡單黎講，你有一筆錢，你而家唔用，放落市場，你期望呢筆錢係將來你用既時候變得更多，呢個就係投資既最根本原因。EOI 推介你買指數基金，用平均成本法分散入市時機，按年齡分配資產等等。呢度講既基本就係，如何欠缺時間研究投資方法的情況下，獲得與市場整體相若的回報。入面仲提及到一Ｄ其它投資應該遵守既原則。<br />\n<br />\n作為一個新手，你首先要知道差唔多乜都唔研究可以獲得幾多回報。然後你先問，點樣獲得比呢個方法更好的回報。不過，呢類方法係唔係之後都一直行之有效，我是有保留的。不過可以作為參考。"},{"pid":"367bd59bcd2f543093852fcac9b45c0169d3bce5","tid":46471,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:52:47.000Z","msg":"中文版叫 投資簡義 商務有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4181b3529a87a11507ab3c5384694caf2c1c684f","tid":46471,"uid":12731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T16:54:38.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"b580e6e8aceaf15270b57ff62f5e8b24726e6419","tid":46471,"uid":27800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T17:01:14.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"a6099ca9169087d56c0d4620333a64062ada733a","tid":46471,"uid":39402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T01:47:18.000Z","msg":"頗耐之前商務買左依本野<br />\n得百幾頁 每頁仲要唔多字<br />\n英文版都係咁?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c76d8039452308819df7f23c9195a50b42384f4","tid":46471,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T01:56:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>頗耐之前商務買左依本野<br />\n得百幾頁 每頁仲要唔多字<br />\n英文版都係咁?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該係 寫序個d 都讚作者寫得短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad4e75627c4f611e0ff0c781753a49fd9a1ce35e","tid":46471,"uid":5537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T02:13:07.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84cd283c2ba4b3fda3c1d9db8cdb2ffb2ce7afdf","tid":46471,"uid":39402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T02:17:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>頗耐之前商務買左依本野<br />\n得百幾頁 每頁仲要唔多字<br />\n英文版都係咁?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該係 寫序個d 都讚作者寫得短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n見巴打你推薦 趁sem break睇晒佢先"},{"pid":"dd22cac1cca6be28f673bce96042f35e861e8d36","tid":46